.DT
window_size
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
window_size

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
window_size -  This is a call back generated by the driver internally to tell us about the window size of the remote machine.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void window_size(int width,
int height)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^width%^RESET%^ - the number of columns
%^BOLD%^height%^RESET%^ - the number of rows

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This is a call back generated by the driver internally to tell us about
the window size of the remote machine.  This information in this is
only used if the terminal is a network type.
.EP

